abstract: The proposal to give the military greater independent authority is aimed at accelerating the fight against the Islamic State and other militant groups.
snippet: The proposal to give the military greater independent authority is aimed at accelerating the fight against the Islamic State and other militant groups.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON â€” The White House is considering giving the Pentagon more independent authority to conduct counterterrorism raids as part of an effort to accelerate the fight against the Islamic State and other militant organizations, administration officials said on Thursday.
